  "text": "Viability was assessed by propidium iodide (PI) exclusion test, for which 10 6 cells were incubated in 0.5 ml RPMI 5 containing 1 g/ml PI for 5 min at room temperature in the dark [CITATION_1] . The percentage of PIstained dead or dying cells was evaluated with a DAS Mikroskop epifluorescence microscope (Leica) equipped with standard filter sets for Hoechst/4Ј,6Ј-diaminidino-2-phenylindole, fluorescein, tetramethylrhodamine, with a band pass filter for fluorescein (527/20) and with phase contrast optics. Cell viability was Ͼ90% (93-95 %).",
